## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical expertise in multi-tenant governance, deployment automation, and Azure-native patterns like Lighthouse, RBAC scoping, Private Link, and centralized monitoring.

## Key Concepts
- Azure Lighthouse for cross-tenant delegation
- Management Groups/subscriptions per tenant pattern
- Least-privilege RBAC scoped to resource groups
- Private Endpoint / Private Link to shared services
- Azure Policy for tagging and governance; per-tenant budgets
- Centralized monitoring via a single Azure Monitor workspace

## Code Example
```javascript
param tenantName string
param location string = resourceGroup().location
param sqlDatabaseId string

resource tenantRG 'Microsoft.Resources/resourceGroups@2021-04-01' = {
  name: 'rg-${tenantName}'
  location: location
}

resource privateEndpoint 'Microsoft.Network/privateEndpoints@2022-07-01' = {
  name: 'pe-${tenantName}-sql'
  location: location
  resourceGroup: tenantRG.name
  properties: {
    subnet: {
      id: subnetId
    }
    privateLinkServiceConnections: [{
      name: 'sql-connection'
      properties: {
        privateLinkServiceId: sqlDatabaseId
        groupIds: ['sqlServer']
      }
    }]
  }
}
```

